The paper discusses the use of deep learning in improving data curation solutions, which involves discovering, integrating, and cleaning data. This topic is closely related to several sub-categories in computer science, including database systems (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and natural language processing (cs.CL). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
